1
00:01:01,110 --> 00:01:02,810
ATTIC CAT
CHAPTER 11

2
00:01:03,675 --> 00:01:05,032
PRODUCED by Woon-hyun Jung

3
00:01:05,966 --> 00:01:07,302
SCRIPT by Hyo-jung Min & Sun-kyung Koo

4
00:01:08,266 --> 00:01:09,936
DIRECTED by Sa-hyun Kim

5
00:02:26,475 --> 00:02:29,476
Kyung-min!

6
00:02:29,476 --> 00:02:31,516
( hello? )

7
00:02:31,516 --> 00:02:33,099
Jung-eun,

8
00:02:33,099 --> 00:02:36,059
it's me.

9
00:02:36,059 --> 00:02:38,892
I got curious about one thing.

10
00:02:38,892 --> 00:02:42,033
what it's like..
'to like somebody'?

11
00:02:42,033 --> 00:02:43,428
I mean,

12
00:02:43,428 --> 00:02:47,418
how do you know
whether you like someone or not?

13
00:02:47,418 --> 00:02:49,267
how?

14
00:02:49,267 --> 00:02:51,413
you don't know about your mind?

15
00:02:51,413 --> 00:02:54,378
maybe I don't.

16
00:02:54,378 --> 00:02:56,555
I think,

17
00:02:56,555 --> 00:03:00,145
I think
I haven't really liked somebody so far..

18
00:03:00,145 --> 00:03:02,683
so I'm very confused now..

19
00:03:03,317 --> 00:03:05,188
confused?

20
00:03:05,188 --> 00:03:07,937
you like Hye-ryun, don't you?

21
00:03:07,937 --> 00:03:10,430
uh?

22
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:11,892
yeah..

23
00:03:11,892 --> 00:03:15,235
right, I like Hye-ryun.

24
00:03:15,235 --> 00:03:16,729
that's right!
I like Hye-ryun!

25
00:03:16,729 --> 00:03:18,990
now it's all clear!
thank you, bye!

26
00:03:49,857 --> 00:03:51,196
ya!

27
00:03:51,196 --> 00:03:53,197
what are you doing here?

28
00:04:19,655 --> 00:04:21,806
you stayed there all night long?

29
00:04:24,308 --> 00:04:26,568
you stayed up there?

30
00:04:26,901 --> 00:04:29,172
I'm asking you,
you stayed up there?

31
00:04:31,221 --> 00:04:33,637
you don't wanna talk to me?

32
00:04:33,637 --> 00:04:36,054
what happened to you?

33
00:04:38,104 --> 00:04:40,413
what is that?

34
00:04:40,413 --> 00:04:42,886
you don't have to mind me anymore.

35
00:04:42,886 --> 00:04:43,933
what?

36
00:04:43,933 --> 00:04:48,259
I'm not interested in you.
I'm not interested in
whom you met & what you've done..etc.

37
00:04:48,259 --> 00:04:50,126
so don't give me a shit any more.

38
00:04:50,126 --> 00:04:51,563
ya..

39
00:04:51,563 --> 00:04:52,796
your chief,

40
00:04:52,796 --> 00:04:55,207
he looks like a nice guy.

41
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:04,713
ya,
it was not like that.
you got it wrong!

42
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,012
did I tell you something?

43
00:05:07,012 --> 00:05:09,787
you got it wrong!
it's really not like that!

44
00:05:09,787 --> 00:05:12,078
I said, I'm not interested
in what you've done.

45
00:05:12,078 --> 00:05:16,288
I've been feeling guilty for you
for all the troubles I made, but now..
I'm free! I don't even feel guilty anymore!

46
00:05:16,288 --> 00:05:18,565
good luck to you.

47
00:05:18,565 --> 00:05:20,089
what?

48
00:05:20,089 --> 00:05:23,796
and I'm giving you an advice as a friend,

49
00:05:23,796 --> 00:05:26,869
don't be an 'easy' girl..
that's not good.

50
00:05:26,869 --> 00:05:29,269
keep that in mind, okay?

51
00:05:29,269 --> 00:05:31,765
you two went too far, huh?

52
00:05:31,765 --> 00:05:34,137
that's not good..

53
00:05:35,607 --> 00:05:37,812
I envy you, Jung-eun.

54
00:05:37,812 --> 00:05:39,381
now your company's like..

55
00:05:39,381 --> 00:05:43,721
buy 1 get 1 free for you!
you can get money, and your love there!

56
00:05:43,721 --> 00:05:45,454
what a happy life for you, huh?

57
00:05:49,468 --> 00:05:53,721
you gotta hurry!
he's waiting for you now!

58
00:05:55,832 --> 00:05:58,201
he's waiting for you, right?

59
00:05:58,201 --> 00:06:00,984
and give my regards to him.

60
00:06:39,239 --> 00:06:41,009
oh, Jung-eun Nam!

61
00:06:42,132 --> 00:06:43,724
good morning.

62
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:46,320
yeah..

63
00:06:53,317 --> 00:06:55,059
uhm..

64
00:07:00,138 --> 00:07:02,338
you didn't hit the button.

65
00:07:23,914 --> 00:07:25,550
hello?

66
00:07:25,550 --> 00:07:26,961
mom,

67
00:07:26,961 --> 00:07:28,387
what's the matter?

68
00:07:28,387 --> 00:07:30,130
the matter is..

69
00:07:30,130 --> 00:07:32,057
the memorandum.

70
00:07:32,057 --> 00:07:33,726
( give it back to me. )

71
00:07:33,726 --> 00:07:36,940
I said, we don't need that kinda thing!

72
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:38,227
mom,

73
00:07:38,227 --> 00:07:40,106
if you ever come again to see him
in his school,

74
00:07:40,106 --> 00:07:43,770
I'll burn up the memorandum!

75
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:46,512
it's working hour now,
bye!

76
00:08:14,714 --> 00:08:15,745
yes?

77
00:08:18,139 --> 00:08:20,402
chief,

78
00:08:23,083 --> 00:08:24,986
I finished my work today,

79
00:08:24,986 --> 00:08:26,892
can I go home now?

80
00:08:26,892 --> 00:08:28,297
if it's okay for you,

81
00:08:28,297 --> 00:08:30,423
let's have dinner together.

82
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:35,652
you got an appointment tonight?

83
00:08:37,564 --> 00:08:38,628
no, I'm free tonight.

84
00:08:38,628 --> 00:08:40,322
let's have dinner together.

85
00:08:40,322 --> 00:08:43,663
I got something to tell you.

86
00:08:43,663 --> 00:08:45,935
okay, let's get out.

87
00:08:47,609 --> 00:08:48,574
what do you like for dinner?

88
00:08:48,574 --> 00:08:50,940
anything's fine.

89
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:52,576
you like lobsters?

90
00:08:52,576 --> 00:08:53,393
yeah.

91
00:08:53,393 --> 00:08:54,945
Jung-eun!

92
00:08:56,709 --> 00:08:57,947
ya,

93
00:08:57,947 --> 00:08:59,175
how come you're here?

94
00:08:59,175 --> 00:09:01,647
I just dropped by.

95
00:09:03,188 --> 00:09:04,370
who is he?

96
00:09:04,370 --> 00:09:06,854
he's my chief.

97
00:09:06,854 --> 00:09:09,329
chief, he's my brother.

98
00:09:10,016 --> 00:09:11,131
how do you do?

99
00:09:11,131 --> 00:09:12,368
how do you do?

100
00:09:12,368 --> 00:09:14,561
my name is Jung-woo Nam.

101
00:09:14,561 --> 00:09:16,574
where are you guys going now?

102
00:09:16,574 --> 00:09:18,699
if it's alright for you,
let's have dinner together.

103
00:09:18,699 --> 00:09:21,859
no, I'll take him to my home.
let's have dinner next time.

104
00:09:21,859 --> 00:09:23,338
no, you don't have to.

105
00:09:23,338 --> 00:09:24,923
I gotta have dinner.

106
00:09:24,923 --> 00:09:26,541
let's go have dinner!

107
00:09:30,208 --> 00:09:31,789
lobster for me, please.

108
00:09:32,682 --> 00:09:34,115
same thing for me.

109
00:09:36,028 --> 00:09:37,455
oh..

110
00:09:41,591 --> 00:09:42,623
well..

111
00:09:42,623 --> 00:09:44,833
do you come here often?

112
00:09:44,833 --> 00:09:46,702
from time to time, yes.

113
00:09:46,702 --> 00:09:49,847
I don't see much resemblance
between you two.

114
00:09:50,569 --> 00:09:51,906
you don't?

115
00:09:51,906 --> 00:09:53,265
everybody's saying that
we're the same shits!

116
00:09:53,265 --> 00:09:54,686
is that right?

117
00:09:56,864 --> 00:09:57,890
by the way,

118
00:09:57,890 --> 00:10:00,861
how many siblings you have?

119
00:10:00,861 --> 00:10:01,876
ya,

120
00:10:01,876 --> 00:10:03,988
why are you asking such a question?

121
00:10:03,988 --> 00:10:06,241
it's okay.

122
00:10:06,241 --> 00:10:08,092
I have one younger sister.

123
00:10:08,092 --> 00:10:11,521
I see..
then you're the only son to your parents.

124
00:10:11,521 --> 00:10:13,223
yes..

125
00:10:15,006 --> 00:10:17,294
are you living together with your parents?

126
00:10:17,294 --> 00:10:18,913
my parents are living in u.s.,

127
00:10:18,913 --> 00:10:21,316
and my sister's in france now,
she's studying there.

128
00:10:21,316 --> 00:10:22,233
oh..

129
00:10:22,233 --> 00:10:24,760
your family is very 'global'!

130
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,737
stop it..

131
00:10:28,571 --> 00:10:29,760
do you mind..

132
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:32,239
if I ask you about your monthly income?

133
00:11:16,410 --> 00:11:18,369
sorry for my brother bothering you.

134
00:11:18,369 --> 00:11:19,883
it's alright.

135
00:11:19,883 --> 00:11:21,850
see you again.

136
00:11:22,636 --> 00:11:24,347
yes.

137
00:11:24,803 --> 00:11:26,591
come see me again.
bye!

138
00:11:26,591 --> 00:11:28,324
yeah, my brother Dong-june!

139
00:11:29,296 --> 00:11:31,021
I'll call you, my brother!

140
00:11:31,021 --> 00:11:32,976
bye my brother, Dong-june!

141
00:11:32,976 --> 00:11:35,122
Dong-june, safe driving, okay?

142
00:11:35,565 --> 00:11:37,133
Dong-june, I love ya!

143
00:11:38,531 --> 00:11:39,903
his 'sedan' is..

144
00:11:39,903 --> 00:11:41,426
shut up!

145
00:11:49,088 --> 00:11:49,634
ya,

146
00:11:49,634 --> 00:11:51,371
why are you doing this to me?

147
00:11:51,371 --> 00:11:52,559
what are you talking bout?

148
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:54,781
you don't have to do this here!

149
00:11:54,781 --> 00:11:56,142
yes, I have to do this.

150
00:11:56,142 --> 00:11:59,026
I'm helping you..

151
00:11:59,026 --> 00:11:59,889
don't you think so?

152
00:12:05,384 --> 00:12:07,271
what are you doing here?

153
00:12:07,271 --> 00:12:09,047
I'm taking some rest.

154
00:12:09,047 --> 00:12:10,122
taking some rest?

155
00:12:10,122 --> 00:12:11,756
that's good.
take your rest there forever!

156
00:12:11,756 --> 00:12:13,676
Jung-eun, let's get inside.

157
00:12:13,676 --> 00:12:17,395
man, it's so hot even in the night.

158
00:12:37,901 --> 00:12:39,073
what did you have for dinner?

159
00:12:39,073 --> 00:12:40,625
did he buy something expensive?

160
00:12:40,625 --> 00:12:42,849
no, we just had 'lobsters'~

161
00:12:42,849 --> 00:12:46,108
he's always buying lobsters.

162
00:12:46,108 --> 00:12:47,534
hey,

163
00:12:47,534 --> 00:12:48,684
don't make your bed here.

164
00:12:48,684 --> 00:12:50,383
why not?

165
00:12:51,426 --> 00:12:52,996
it's cool outside.

166
00:12:52,996 --> 00:12:54,895
you sleep outside.

167
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,052
well,

168
00:12:59,052 --> 00:13:01,703
there has been some misunderstanding between us.

169
00:13:01,703 --> 00:13:02,775
yeah,

170
00:13:02,775 --> 00:13:04,480
I admit that.

171
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:07,198
I admit that
you & my sister are just friends.

172
00:13:07,198 --> 00:13:09,013
and there hasn't been nothing between you two.

173
00:13:09,013 --> 00:13:10,887
yeah, I admit that.

174
00:13:10,887 --> 00:13:13,812
so it's all in the past.

175
00:13:13,812 --> 00:13:18,470
you don't ever come to
my sister's home again, okay?

176
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:24,196
how can you do this to me?

177
00:13:24,196 --> 00:13:25,964
you're not my brother-in-law, right?

178
00:13:25,964 --> 00:13:27,938
you are just a stranger to me!
har har har~

179
00:13:29,247 --> 00:13:30,828
Jung-eun,

180
00:13:30,828 --> 00:13:31,789
Jung-eun Nam!

181
00:13:31,789 --> 00:13:33,318
Jung-eun!

182
00:13:35,422 --> 00:13:36,088
what?

183
00:13:36,088 --> 00:13:37,670
your brother..

184
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:39,862
wants me to get out.

185
00:13:44,812 --> 00:13:46,694
you can get out then.

186
00:13:55,431 --> 00:13:57,807
Jung-eun,
I'm getting outta here!

187
00:14:02,146 --> 00:14:04,530
I'm really getting out!
don't call me back again!

188
00:14:51,629 --> 00:14:52,853
wake up.

189
00:14:54,232 --> 00:14:56,524
wake up!

190
00:14:57,561 --> 00:14:58,534
what..

191
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:01,084
I said, wake up!

192
00:15:02,567 --> 00:15:05,736
uh..good bye.
leave me alone..

193
00:15:06,312 --> 00:15:08,043
I said, wake up!

194
00:15:08,043 --> 00:15:10,521
why why why why!

195
00:15:10,981 --> 00:15:13,059
don't raise your voice to me.

196
00:15:14,221 --> 00:15:15,401
hey,

197
00:15:15,401 --> 00:15:18,067
let me ask you one question.

198
00:15:18,067 --> 00:15:22,076
when are you gonna get out of my sister's place?

199
00:15:22,076 --> 00:15:23,389
what?

200
00:15:23,389 --> 00:15:25,660
please have some manners.

201
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:27,522
you're living off my sister now, right?

202
00:15:27,522 --> 00:15:29,147
so get outta this place ASAP.

203
00:15:29,147 --> 00:15:30,941
what did you just say?

204
00:15:30,941 --> 00:15:34,478
what a mean guy you are..

205
00:15:37,161 --> 00:15:38,192
let's go.

206
00:16:32,687 --> 00:16:33,661
ya,

207
00:16:33,661 --> 00:16:34,997
what the hell is this?

208
00:16:34,997 --> 00:16:36,432
you came?

209
00:16:36,432 --> 00:16:38,868
as you can see, this is a tent.

210
00:16:38,868 --> 00:16:40,833
where did you get this?

211
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:41,814
you bought this?

212
00:16:41,814 --> 00:16:44,703
yeah, I bought it.
you can't get it for free.

213
00:16:44,703 --> 00:16:47,055
where did you get the money for this?

214
00:16:47,700 --> 00:16:50,232
I took 30,000 won from the kitchen..

215
00:16:50,232 --> 00:16:53,249
and some more money from your drawer.

216
00:16:53,249 --> 00:16:55,098
what?

217
00:16:55,617 --> 00:16:58,829
you must be crazy!
that's our living expenses for this month!

218
00:17:00,132 --> 00:17:02,023
I know, but..

219
00:17:02,023 --> 00:17:04,073
you guys were behaving so mean.

220
00:17:04,073 --> 00:17:06,935
so there's nothing I can do.
I need some place to sleep in.

221
00:17:25,928 --> 00:17:27,095
what're ya doing?

222
00:17:27,095 --> 00:17:28,510
ya ya!

223
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:32,520
stop reading the book.

224
00:17:33,898 --> 00:17:37,351
peel garlic
until you make up the money for this tent.

225
00:17:37,351 --> 00:17:38,356
no, I won't.

226
00:17:38,356 --> 00:17:39,716
yes, you will!

227
00:17:39,716 --> 00:17:41,562
no, I won't!

228
00:17:46,659 --> 00:17:47,554
ya!

229
00:17:47,554 --> 00:17:49,271
what?

230
00:17:49,271 --> 00:17:51,259
put the garlic into basket.

231
00:17:51,259 --> 00:17:53,365
no, I won't.

232
00:17:53,365 --> 00:17:55,228
wanna see me getting mad?

233
00:17:55,228 --> 00:17:58,079
no, I don't..
and I won't peel garlic, either.

234
00:18:10,582 --> 00:18:11,288
ya!

235
00:18:11,288 --> 00:18:12,784
what?

236
00:18:13,924 --> 00:18:17,924
I'll make you bald
without a single piece of hair!

237
00:18:17,924 --> 00:18:20,096
are you behaving like this
when you're with your chief?

238
00:18:20,096 --> 00:18:21,258
what?

239
00:18:21,258 --> 00:18:23,662
if he had seen you like this,

240
00:18:23,662 --> 00:18:27,096
he'd just hate you!

241
00:18:31,689 --> 00:18:33,413
oh, my hair..

242
00:18:46,457 --> 00:18:48,621
Kyung-min,
go check the test result on the board.

243
00:18:49,096 --> 00:18:52,164
oh I forgot,
is the result on the board?

244
00:18:52,164 --> 00:18:54,118
- how about you? you checked your score?
- yeah,

245
00:18:54,118 --> 00:18:57,372
by the way,
your answer sheets are on the board.

246
00:18:57,372 --> 00:18:59,032
you buy me a drink!

247
00:18:59,032 --> 00:19:01,641
my answer sheets on the board?
why?

248
00:19:03,578 --> 00:19:05,080
( criminal law & bla bla bla.. )

249
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:08,285
who's got the highest score this time?

250
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:13,493
Kyung-min,

251
00:19:13,493 --> 00:19:14,546
you got the highest score?

252
00:19:14,546 --> 00:19:18,038
oh well,
it's not the real exam, you know.
it was just a trial test.

253
00:19:18,038 --> 00:19:19,703
it's nothing!

254
00:19:19,703 --> 00:19:22,586
what really matters is..
the real bar exam!

255
00:19:22,586 --> 00:19:24,556
this test doesn't mean anything!

256
00:19:24,556 --> 00:19:25,729
shut up.

257
00:19:26,291 --> 00:19:29,028
my score is lower than I thought it to be..
bye!

258
00:19:30,067 --> 00:19:31,530
granma,

259
00:19:31,530 --> 00:19:33,998
I had my test score.

260
00:19:33,998 --> 00:19:37,404
well,

261
00:19:37,404 --> 00:19:42,643
I got the highest score
among present & past & future students!

262
00:19:42,643 --> 00:19:44,819
party? oh no!

263
00:19:44,819 --> 00:19:45,510
toda..

264
00:19:46,345 --> 00:19:50,387
I can't come to your place today..

265
00:19:50,387 --> 00:19:52,887
uh..see you next week, okay?

266
00:19:52,887 --> 00:19:54,124
bye!

267
00:19:56,357 --> 00:19:57,900
Jung-eun~

268
00:20:02,814 --> 00:20:04,568
chief,

269
00:20:06,030 --> 00:20:08,476
are you free tonight?

270
00:20:08,476 --> 00:20:10,738
I got something to tell you.

271
00:20:11,377 --> 00:20:12,310
I'm okay.

272
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:13,939
let's go.

273
00:20:17,259 --> 00:20:19,274
your brother's not coming today?

274
00:20:19,274 --> 00:20:20,415
no.

275
00:20:21,688 --> 00:20:22,679
hello?

276
00:20:22,679 --> 00:20:24,721
Jung-eun,
you're in your office?

277
00:20:24,721 --> 00:20:26,420
now I'm at the lobby of..

278
00:20:35,108 --> 00:20:37,166
how come you're here?

279
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:38,525
oh,

280
00:20:38,525 --> 00:20:40,870
I was just passing by.

281
00:20:40,870 --> 00:20:42,469
how are you?

282
00:20:42,469 --> 00:20:44,621
how are you doing?

283
00:20:46,180 --> 00:20:47,917
you finished your work today?

284
00:20:47,917 --> 00:20:49,322
yeah, but..

285
00:20:49,322 --> 00:20:52,324
I gotta have dinner with my chief.

286
00:20:52,324 --> 00:20:53,882
if it's okay for you,
let's have dinner together.

287
00:20:53,882 --> 00:20:56,102
Kyung-min, you go home first.

288
00:20:56,102 --> 00:20:58,519
me & my chief have something to talk about.

289
00:21:04,330 --> 00:21:06,061
we can have some talk next time.

290
00:21:06,061 --> 00:21:07,432
let's go have dinner together.

291
00:21:07,432 --> 00:21:08,652
no,

292
00:21:08,652 --> 00:21:10,234
you guys can go without me.

293
00:21:10,234 --> 00:21:13,405
'cause I'm a busy guy.

294
00:21:29,851 --> 00:21:31,618
see you next time.

295
00:21:31,618 --> 00:21:33,250
yeah.

296
00:21:34,103 --> 00:21:35,722
see you later.

297
00:21:35,722 --> 00:21:37,822
okay, have a good one.

298
00:21:39,096 --> 00:21:40,062
excuse us.

299
00:21:49,585 --> 00:21:52,951
are they going to have steaks?

300
00:21:59,263 --> 00:22:00,841
I've got the highest score..

301
00:22:09,538 --> 00:22:12,068
what do you wanna have for dinner?
you have something on your mind?

302
00:22:12,068 --> 00:22:14,337
anything's fine for me.

303
00:22:18,041 --> 00:22:19,070
what?

304
00:22:19,070 --> 00:22:22,013
I'm gonna have a sam-gyop-sal(pork-belly) 
party tonight.
join me or not, it's up to you!

305
00:22:27,203 --> 00:22:29,246
can we really go?

306
00:22:30,691 --> 00:22:32,583
yes.

307
00:24:33,251 --> 00:24:34,748
so..

308
00:24:34,748 --> 00:24:36,945
your brother's back home?

309
00:24:38,186 --> 00:24:40,959
why did you do that to me?

310
00:24:40,959 --> 00:24:42,923
what?

311
00:24:42,923 --> 00:24:45,292
I think I should've slapped on your face.

312
00:24:45,292 --> 00:24:47,325
but I was so stunned back then.

313
00:24:48,963 --> 00:24:50,719
we were drunk at that time.

314
00:24:50,719 --> 00:24:53,621
so I can forgive you about last time, but..

315
00:24:53,621 --> 00:24:56,798
I don't want you to do that to me again.

316
00:24:56,798 --> 00:24:58,343
well,

317
00:24:58,343 --> 00:25:00,075
I like you..

318
00:25:00,075 --> 00:25:01,895
so much.

319
00:25:01,895 --> 00:25:04,182
what?

320
00:25:05,138 --> 00:25:07,206
I told you that,
'how about me as your boyfriend?'

321
00:25:07,206 --> 00:25:08,543
you remember?

322
00:25:08,543 --> 00:25:10,681
that was not a joke.

323
00:25:13,512 --> 00:25:14,790
oh,

324
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:16,218
I'm just..

325
00:25:16,218 --> 00:25:18,412
you don't have to answer me right now.

326
00:25:18,412 --> 00:25:20,025
think it over and..

327
00:25:20,025 --> 00:25:22,328
answer me later.

328
00:26:36,460 --> 00:26:38,694
Jung-eun..

329
00:27:06,606 --> 00:27:08,826
I gotta go out after breakfast.

330
00:27:11,701 --> 00:27:14,100
so peel all the garlic
before I come back, okay?

331
00:27:15,005 --> 00:27:17,748
I'd rather get outta this place
than peel garlic!

332
00:27:18,370 --> 00:27:20,511
do as you please.

333
00:27:20,511 --> 00:27:22,921
yeah, I'll do as I please!

334
00:27:38,010 --> 00:27:40,731
you want me to peel garlic?
I WON'T!

335
00:27:42,035 --> 00:27:45,530
I told Kyung-min to come back home until today.
but he hasn't come back yet.

336
00:27:45,530 --> 00:27:48,406
he'll come back with the memorandum.

337
00:27:48,406 --> 00:27:51,824
he still hasn't got the memorandum back.
and he's still hanging around outside home..

338
00:27:51,824 --> 00:27:53,880
oh, what's going on now?

339
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:56,849
don't worry.
he promised to get the memorandum back to us.

340
00:27:56,849 --> 00:28:02,773
are they really 'just' friends?
what if they're living together as lovers?

341
00:28:02,773 --> 00:28:04,191
oh..

342
00:28:04,191 --> 00:28:08,086
she's way below
Kyung-min's own standard of girls.

343
00:28:08,086 --> 00:28:10,105
just let them be.

344
00:28:10,105 --> 00:28:12,367
Kyung-min has nothing to lose.
but she has something to lose.

345
00:28:12,367 --> 00:28:16,545
Kyung-min stamped on it
because he has such a weak character!

346
00:28:16,545 --> 00:28:21,797
that means he might do something worse!

347
00:28:28,465 --> 00:28:30,691
Kyung-min, you're home?

348
00:28:31,253 --> 00:28:32,693
oh, mother!

349
00:28:32,693 --> 00:28:34,226
glad you came here.

350
00:28:36,068 --> 00:28:37,393
what are you doing now?

351
00:28:37,393 --> 00:28:40,094
- well,
- you are peeling garlic?

352
00:28:40,094 --> 00:28:44,070
you're an exam student!
how come you aren't studying now?

353
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,263
you gave up the bar exam?

354
00:28:45,263 --> 00:28:46,574
no, I didn't give it up.

355
00:28:46,574 --> 00:28:49,272
garlic is for some extra bucks.

356
00:28:50,172 --> 00:28:52,262
what is that tent?

357
00:28:52,262 --> 00:28:54,114
oh..

358
00:28:56,021 --> 00:29:00,446
I want some camping atmosphere.
that helps me to concentrate on my study.

359
00:29:00,446 --> 00:29:04,564
study in the tent?
wake up, you're an exam student!

360
00:29:05,529 --> 00:29:06,911
where's Jung-eun?

361
00:29:06,911 --> 00:29:09,287
she's off to the bank.

362
00:29:09,287 --> 00:29:10,122
oh yeah?

363
00:29:10,122 --> 00:29:11,894
let's get inside & have some talk.

364
00:29:11,894 --> 00:29:13,166
yeah.

365
00:29:21,241 --> 00:29:22,873
oh..what are you doing?

366
00:29:22,873 --> 00:29:25,970
I'm helping you packing up your things.

367
00:29:25,970 --> 00:29:28,086
these are your things, right?

368
00:29:28,942 --> 00:29:32,511
right, but..

369
00:29:32,511 --> 00:29:34,561
mother, Jung-eun hasn't come back yet.

370
00:29:34,561 --> 00:29:36,251
you can wait 'til she comes back.

371
00:29:37,419 --> 00:29:39,820
you shouldn't call me 'mother'.

372
00:29:39,820 --> 00:29:43,226
people will misunderstand it.
can you stop calling me 'mother'?

373
00:29:43,493 --> 00:29:44,861
let's pack up.

374
00:29:51,861 --> 00:29:54,612
you go first with this bag.
I'll send the rest of your things by the postal service.

375
00:29:55,171 --> 00:29:56,773
oh mother,

376
00:29:56,773 --> 00:29:57,854
I can't go.

377
00:29:57,854 --> 00:29:59,973
you can't?
why not?

378
00:29:59,973 --> 00:30:01,993
at least I have to say goodbye to Jung-eun.

379
00:30:01,993 --> 00:30:04,157
goodbye?
you can say goodbye by phone!

380
00:30:04,157 --> 00:30:05,324
- mother!
- go away!

381
00:30:05,324 --> 00:30:06,743
mother!
I'm not prepared for leaving this place..

382
00:30:12,523 --> 00:30:13,670
mom!

383
00:30:13,670 --> 00:30:15,523
what are you doing here?

384
00:30:15,523 --> 00:30:17,701
Jung-eun!

385
00:30:18,102 --> 00:30:19,933
he wants to leave this place.
so I'm helping him out.

386
00:30:19,933 --> 00:30:21,252
no! I'm not leaving here.

387
00:30:23,368 --> 00:30:25,133
you get inside with your bag.

388
00:30:25,133 --> 00:30:26,430
I'm okay here.

389
00:30:26,430 --> 00:30:27,932
I said, get inside!

390
00:30:27,932 --> 00:30:29,080
okay.

391
00:30:43,729 --> 00:30:45,357
what the hell you're doing here, mom?

392
00:30:45,357 --> 00:30:48,486
getting him out of this place.

393
00:30:48,486 --> 00:30:50,132
getting him outta this place?
why?

394
00:30:50,132 --> 00:30:52,164
what if your chief got to know about it?

395
00:30:52,164 --> 00:30:54,900
he'll misunderstand it!

396
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:56,067
my chief?

397
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:59,202
mom, he's just my chief,
not my boyfriend!

398
00:30:59,202 --> 00:31:01,400
I heard that you're going out with him.

399
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:04,303
and Kyung-min got angry about that.

400
00:31:04,303 --> 00:31:06,852
you heard it from Jung-woo?

401
00:31:06,852 --> 00:31:09,147
he's always making stories!
don't you know that?

402
00:31:09,147 --> 00:31:11,209
anyway,

403
00:31:11,209 --> 00:31:12,708
you shouldn't live with him.

404
00:31:12,708 --> 00:31:13,949
you two are not gonna get married, right?

405
00:31:13,949 --> 00:31:17,008
why are you still with him?
you should let him go.

406
00:31:17,008 --> 00:31:18,319
no,

407
00:31:18,319 --> 00:31:19,870
I can't let him go.

408
00:31:19,870 --> 00:31:21,692
you can't?
why not?

409
00:31:21,692 --> 00:31:23,899
why you can't let him go?

410
00:31:23,899 --> 00:31:26,897
mom,

411
00:31:26,897 --> 00:31:30,827
I can't live without him!

412
00:31:30,827 --> 00:31:32,844
( what did you just say? )

413
00:31:47,033 --> 00:31:49,631
I gotta go now.

414
00:31:49,631 --> 00:31:52,524
don't peel garlic any more and..

415
00:31:52,524 --> 00:31:55,092
concentrate on your study, understand?

416
00:31:56,138 --> 00:31:59,202
you don't answer me?

417
00:31:59,202 --> 00:32:01,300
yes, mother.
I'll study hard.

418
00:32:04,007 --> 00:32:06,885
good bye. take care.

419
00:32:08,445 --> 00:32:10,007
mom,

420
00:32:21,544 --> 00:32:23,287
Jung-eun,

421
00:32:23,287 --> 00:32:25,561
it's good to be back in my room.

422
00:32:25,561 --> 00:32:29,572
it's not a good idea
to change the place where you sleep.

423
00:32:29,572 --> 00:32:32,341
it's cool outside, but..

424
00:32:32,341 --> 00:32:37,508
too many mosquitoes!
see this?

425
00:32:47,281 --> 00:32:49,417
ya!
you're sleeping?

426
00:32:51,227 --> 00:32:53,861
the tent is..

427
00:32:53,861 --> 00:32:56,957
I don't think we can get the refund of it, so..

428
00:32:56,957 --> 00:33:01,109
let's keep it until I pass the bar exam.
I'll take you to a vacation with it, okay?

429
00:33:01,109 --> 00:33:02,497
and,

430
00:33:02,497 --> 00:33:04,140
I'm not gonna peel garlic any more.

431
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,535
your mom wants me to..

432
00:33:05,535 --> 00:33:09,261
stop peeling garlic
and concentrate on my study.

433
00:33:09,261 --> 00:33:11,337
okay?

434
00:33:14,550 --> 00:33:16,044
ya!

435
00:33:16,044 --> 00:33:18,880
shut up and sleep.

436
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,290
okay, Jug-eun.

437
00:33:20,290 --> 00:33:22,256
sleep tight, Jung-eun!

438
00:33:32,990 --> 00:33:34,531
Jung-eun,

439
00:33:34,531 --> 00:33:37,533
I forgot to tell you this.
I got the highest score from a test!

440
00:33:38,833 --> 00:33:39,672
oh,

441
00:33:39,672 --> 00:33:41,361
maybe it's not a big thing, but..

442
00:33:41,361 --> 00:33:44,291
I wanna let you know about it,
that's all.

443
00:34:22,081 --> 00:34:23,203
oh..

444
00:34:23,203 --> 00:34:25,480
what am I gonna eat?

445
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:27,898
I can't find anything good.

446
00:34:27,898 --> 00:34:28,985
you can't?

447
00:34:28,985 --> 00:34:32,860
then you can peel garlic
or eat your tent.

448
00:34:37,344 --> 00:34:38,859
hello?

449
00:34:38,859 --> 00:34:41,083
chief!

450
00:34:41,887 --> 00:34:46,338
you remember the plant you gave to me?

451
00:34:46,338 --> 00:34:48,202
yes,

452
00:34:54,307 --> 00:34:57,009
you promised to find a name of it.

453
00:34:57,009 --> 00:34:58,382
what's its name?

454
00:34:58,382 --> 00:35:00,740
I don't know it yet.

455
00:35:00,740 --> 00:35:02,883
sorry.

456
00:35:02,883 --> 00:35:05,247
by the way,

457
00:35:05,247 --> 00:35:08,509
are you doing anything this afternoon?

458
00:35:10,526 --> 00:35:12,476
okay, see you there.

459
00:35:20,768 --> 00:35:22,134
ya,

460
00:35:22,134 --> 00:35:24,788
you hate this cat so much.

461
00:35:24,788 --> 00:35:26,431
no, I don't~

462
00:35:26,431 --> 00:35:29,263
I don't get why cat hates cat.

463
00:35:29,263 --> 00:35:30,489
what?

464
00:35:30,489 --> 00:35:32,104
no, nothing.

465
00:35:36,063 --> 00:35:37,448
ya,

466
00:35:37,448 --> 00:35:40,749
what does your chief think you are?
a toy for him?

467
00:35:40,749 --> 00:35:43,251
he's always calling you up when he's get bored.

468
00:35:43,251 --> 00:35:44,859
what?

469
00:35:44,859 --> 00:35:50,060
he shouldn't do that.
people will misunderstand it.

470
00:35:50,060 --> 00:35:52,358
don't worry.
I can handle it.

471
00:35:52,358 --> 00:35:54,905
yeah, I know you can handle it, but..

472
00:35:54,905 --> 00:35:58,689
I mean,
I hope you not to have dinner with him..

473
00:35:58,689 --> 00:36:06,055
and not to get on his car..etc.
in short, you better not see him privately!

474
00:36:10,194 --> 00:36:12,235
and he did that to him, right?

475
00:36:12,235 --> 00:36:14,399
uh?

476
00:36:14,399 --> 00:36:16,289
what do you mean?

477
00:36:19,024 --> 00:36:20,558
I don't know.

478
00:36:20,558 --> 00:36:22,327
I can't remember.

479
00:36:22,327 --> 00:36:24,964
oh, you were drunk at that time?

480
00:36:24,964 --> 00:36:27,038
that's why he's a playboy!

481
00:36:27,038 --> 00:36:29,313
making you drunk and do that to you?

482
00:36:29,313 --> 00:36:33,043
oh, what a..
anyway, don't spend time with him anymore.

483
00:36:33,043 --> 00:36:34,536
understand?

484
00:36:35,775 --> 00:36:36,519
ya,

485
00:36:36,519 --> 00:36:37,885
you understand what I'm saying?

486
00:36:38,556 --> 00:36:40,813
have your breakfast.

487
00:36:48,803 --> 00:36:51,822
it's gonna rain in the afternoon.
collect the laundry when it rains.

488
00:36:51,822 --> 00:36:53,082
I'm going out!

489
00:36:53,082 --> 00:36:56,665
I don't care about
whom you're gonna see!

490
00:37:00,959 --> 00:37:02,203
ya!

491
00:37:02,203 --> 00:37:04,120
I'm not gonna collect 'em!

492
00:37:04,120 --> 00:37:06,203
come back before 6!

493
00:37:06,203 --> 00:37:08,733
don't drink with him again!
Jung-eun, come home early..

494
00:37:08,733 --> 00:37:10,518
Jung-eun..

495
00:37:18,444 --> 00:37:19,580
how about some wine?

496
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:21,424
no, thanks.

497
00:37:21,424 --> 00:37:23,498
a cup of coffee for me.

498
00:37:23,764 --> 00:37:25,532
I'll take wine.

499
00:37:29,192 --> 00:37:30,998
you said you've got something to tell me.
what is it?

500
00:37:38,306 --> 00:37:42,607
oh, you don't have to find
the name of the plant you gave to me.

501
00:37:42,607 --> 00:37:44,386
I named it.

502
00:37:44,386 --> 00:37:46,514
'my Jung-eun'

503
00:37:46,514 --> 00:37:48,290
I'm sorry?

504
00:37:48,290 --> 00:37:50,890
I named it 'my Jung-eun'.

505
00:37:50,890 --> 00:37:52,672
it's very country-style..

506
00:37:52,672 --> 00:37:54,121
just like you.

507
00:37:54,121 --> 00:37:56,459
chief,

508
00:37:56,459 --> 00:38:00,093
I gotta tell you something.

509
00:38:02,950 --> 00:38:04,771
I think I gotta give it back to you.

510
00:38:04,771 --> 00:38:09,607
'cause the cat at my home
hates this cat so much.

511
00:38:09,607 --> 00:38:11,889
I don't think I can keep it.

512
00:38:11,889 --> 00:38:13,943
so I'm giving it back to you.

513
00:38:15,047 --> 00:38:19,716
no matter how many rough times
it gives to me,

514
00:38:19,716 --> 00:38:24,538
the cat at my home is
the most important one to me.

515
00:38:24,538 --> 00:38:26,838
I don't think I can raise..

516
00:38:26,838 --> 00:38:30,097
another cat.

517
00:38:35,432 --> 00:38:37,339
I'm sorry to tell you this.

518
00:40:01,221 --> 00:40:02,953
Jung-eun, Jung-eun!

519
00:40:02,953 --> 00:40:04,672
Jung-eun!

520
00:40:05,600 --> 00:40:08,528
were you waiting for me?

521
00:40:08,528 --> 00:40:09,572
you can give a call!

522
00:40:09,572 --> 00:40:11,060
I told you to come back before 6.

523
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:12,099
your umbrella.

524
00:40:12,099 --> 00:40:13,739
thanks.

525
00:40:14,499 --> 00:40:15,548
ya!

526
00:40:15,548 --> 00:40:16,604
it's broken!

527
00:40:16,604 --> 00:40:18,437
but yours is good one!

528
00:40:18,437 --> 00:40:20,521
no, yours is good one too!

529
00:40:21,879 --> 00:40:23,140
okay, let me have yours.

530
00:40:27,013 --> 00:40:29,152
let's use it together.

531
00:40:54,422 --> 00:40:56,077
Kyung-min,

532
00:41:00,083 --> 00:41:01,607
Kyung-min Lee!

533
00:41:02,245 --> 00:41:03,815
oh, Hye-ryun!

534
00:41:03,815 --> 00:41:04,950
Hye-ryun,

535
00:41:04,950 --> 00:41:06,689
you can't even hear me calling you?

536
00:41:06,689 --> 00:41:09,572
oh, I lost myself in the book..

537
00:41:09,572 --> 00:41:11,666
I heard that you got the highest score
from the test.

538
00:41:11,666 --> 00:41:13,360
congratulations!

539
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:15,154
oh, it's just a trial test.

540
00:41:15,154 --> 00:41:16,563
you can buy me a drink.

541
00:41:16,563 --> 00:41:18,209
good, I'll buy you a drink.

542
00:41:18,209 --> 00:41:19,776
how about tonight?

543
00:41:20,244 --> 00:41:22,112
well, today is..

544
00:41:22,112 --> 00:41:24,891
why?
you've got an appointment?

545
00:41:24,891 --> 00:41:26,178
sort of.

546
00:41:26,178 --> 00:41:29,064
my granma told me to come home early tonight.

547
00:41:29,064 --> 00:41:30,707
that's alright.

548
00:41:30,707 --> 00:41:31,939
how about tomorrow, then?

549
00:41:31,939 --> 00:41:34,686
tomorrow's okay.
I'll buy you decent dinner!

550
00:41:34,686 --> 00:41:36,227
good, see you tomorrow.

551
00:41:36,227 --> 00:41:37,720
see ya.

552
00:41:53,769 --> 00:41:55,145
Kyung-min,

553
00:41:55,145 --> 00:41:57,538
I'll drive you home.

554
00:41:57,538 --> 00:41:58,506
drive me home?

555
00:41:58,506 --> 00:42:00,141
let's go.

556
00:42:00,141 --> 00:42:02,515
Hye-ryun,
I gotta finish this book..

557
00:42:02,515 --> 00:42:03,678
get up,
I'll take you home.

558
00:42:03,678 --> 00:42:05,279
oh, I'm..

559
00:42:06,096 --> 00:42:07,558
okay.

560
00:42:14,457 --> 00:42:16,625
I guess your granma's very happy
with you back home.

561
00:42:16,625 --> 00:42:18,090
yes, she is.

562
00:42:18,090 --> 00:42:20,735
she wants to thank you
'cause you took me back to home.

563
00:42:20,735 --> 00:42:23,122
you wanna get in and see her?

564
00:42:23,122 --> 00:42:23,967
sounds good.

565
00:42:23,967 --> 00:42:26,234
okay, let's get inside.

566
00:42:26,234 --> 00:42:28,221
Hye-ryun!

567
00:42:28,221 --> 00:42:31,340
oh I forgot
we're having some guests tonight.

568
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:34,879
my granma's very busy now.

569
00:42:34,879 --> 00:42:37,855
you can see her next time.
thank you for driving me home, bye!

570
00:42:37,855 --> 00:42:39,513
you're weird today.

571
00:42:39,513 --> 00:42:41,471
weird?

572
00:42:42,303 --> 00:42:43,536
never mind.

573
00:42:43,536 --> 00:42:44,549
bye.

574
00:42:44,549 --> 00:42:46,798
bye, Hye-ryun!

575
00:42:47,706 --> 00:42:48,523
take care!

576
00:43:14,021 --> 00:43:15,220
Jung-eun!

577
00:43:15,220 --> 00:43:17,724
you said you're almost home.
how come it took so long?

578
00:43:17,724 --> 00:43:22,023
the traffic jam was so tough!
oh..the bus wasn't moving!

579
00:43:22,023 --> 00:43:23,659
traffic jam at dinner time is tough.

580
00:43:23,659 --> 00:43:25,770
this chige(=stew) got little bit thick.

581
00:43:25,770 --> 00:43:28,237
it's alright for me.

582
00:43:29,367 --> 00:43:30,745
what happened to your right hand?

583
00:43:31,340 --> 00:43:33,737
I've been studying
holding a pencil all day loooong.

584
00:43:33,737 --> 00:43:36,167
I can't even hold a spoon now.
my right hand is aching!

585
00:43:36,167 --> 00:43:38,235
don't lie to me.

586
00:43:38,235 --> 00:43:42,293
it's true!
from 9 a.m., I've been holding a pencil like this..
ouch..

587
00:43:43,444 --> 00:43:44,513
I don't think I can hold my spoon.

588
00:43:44,513 --> 00:43:45,952
you feed me, ah~

589
00:43:47,258 --> 00:43:50,061
I'm hungry. feed me.
I can't use my right hand.

590
00:43:51,822 --> 00:43:53,429
you're so funny.

591
00:43:53,429 --> 00:43:55,422
I'm hungry.
ah~~

592
00:43:58,443 --> 00:44:00,371
I want ham first.

593
00:44:02,308 --> 00:44:03,318
with ketchup!

594
00:44:12,507 --> 00:44:13,739
Hye-ryun..

595
00:44:15,581 --> 00:44:17,215
why did you come here again?

596
00:44:20,769 --> 00:44:23,623
you guys are so funny, huh?

597
00:44:23,623 --> 00:44:25,692
Hye-ryun, my hand is aching..

598
00:44:27,291 --> 00:44:28,903
Hye-ryun!

599
00:44:28,903 --> 00:44:29,901
where are you going?

600
00:44:29,901 --> 00:44:32,272
Hye-ryun!

601
00:44:33,881 --> 00:44:35,107
- wait up,
- get off me!

602
00:44:35,735 --> 00:44:36,813
let me explain.

603
00:44:36,813 --> 00:44:38,545
I don't wanna hear from you!

604
00:44:40,070 --> 00:44:43,881
I came here just to have dinner with her,
because she said she's bored home alone..

605
00:44:43,881 --> 00:44:45,077
Kyung-min Lee,

606
00:44:45,077 --> 00:44:46,848
uh?

607
00:44:46,848 --> 00:44:49,257
game is over with you!

608
00:44:55,557 --> 00:44:56,622
Hye-ryun,
you're misunderstanding something!

609
00:45:16,715 --> 00:45:18,221
don't ever call me again.

610
00:45:18,221 --> 00:45:20,210
it's all over!

611
00:45:22,011 --> 00:45:23,688
hello..hello?
Hye-ryun!

612
00:45:43,586 --> 00:45:45,403
what am I supposed to do?

613
00:46:18,279 --> 00:46:19,738
Hye-ryun,

614
00:46:20,383 --> 00:46:22,851
let me explain the situation,

615
00:46:22,851 --> 00:46:24,398
( you misunderstood something. )

616
00:46:24,398 --> 00:46:29,153
no, I don't wanna hear you
lying to me again.

617
00:46:29,153 --> 00:46:31,692
Hye-ryun, I'm not lying to you.

618
00:46:31,692 --> 00:46:36,299
I can't believe you any more.
so, if you wanna recover our relationship,
tell Jung-eun to come to me and explain the situation.

619
00:46:36,299 --> 00:46:37,726
uh?

620
00:46:37,726 --> 00:46:39,104
nothing more to say to you.

621
00:46:39,104 --> 00:46:40,963
I'm not very patient, so..

622
00:46:40,963 --> 00:46:42,513
it's up to you now.

623
00:47:40,162 --> 00:47:41,486
( Kyung-min, )

624
00:47:44,563 --> 00:47:46,979
( hello, )

625
00:47:46,979 --> 00:47:48,447
( hello? )

626
00:47:59,996 --> 00:48:02,377
one more bottle of soju here!

627
00:48:09,407 --> 00:48:10,843
Kyung-min!

628
00:48:13,927 --> 00:48:15,016
Kyung-min!

629
00:48:21,275 --> 00:48:23,223
you're drunk?

630
00:48:23,223 --> 00:48:24,638
yeah, I'm drunk.

631
00:48:25,347 --> 00:48:27,204
let's go home.

632
00:48:34,892 --> 00:48:36,847
sit down.

633
00:48:42,497 --> 00:48:44,563
where have you been?

634
00:48:45,936 --> 00:48:49,066
I've been to Hye-ryun's home..

635
00:48:49,066 --> 00:48:50,679
oh yeah?

636
00:48:51,732 --> 00:48:53,408
what did she say to you?

637
00:48:53,408 --> 00:48:54,935
uh?

638
00:48:54,935 --> 00:48:56,771
I don't know...

639
00:48:56,771 --> 00:48:58,582
she doesn't wanna talk to me.

640
00:48:58,582 --> 00:49:02,488
see?
she's very sharp tempered.
I told you before.

641
00:49:02,488 --> 00:49:03,970
no..

642
00:49:12,759 --> 00:49:14,085
what?

643
00:49:24,943 --> 00:49:26,941
Jung-eun..

644
00:49:29,070 --> 00:49:32,676
can you do just one favor for me?

645
00:49:32,676 --> 00:49:36,058
what kind of favor?

646
00:49:36,058 --> 00:49:39,241
can you go to see Hye-ryun and..

647
00:49:39,241 --> 00:49:43,114
tell her that we're just friends..

648
00:49:43,114 --> 00:49:48,157
and I like noboby but Hye-ryun..
can't you do that for me?

649
00:49:50,387 --> 00:49:52,824
what did you just say?

650
00:49:56,654 --> 00:49:58,573
are you insane?

651
00:49:58,573 --> 00:50:01,373
why do I have to tell
that sort of things to Hye-ryun?

652
00:50:01,373 --> 00:50:04,099
oh..

653
00:50:04,099 --> 00:50:06,554
but you're my friend, aren't you?

654
00:50:06,554 --> 00:50:07,676
last time,

655
00:50:07,676 --> 00:50:10,977
I stamped on the memorandum for you
as a friend..

656
00:50:10,977 --> 00:50:15,059
can't you return the favor?

657
00:50:17,093 --> 00:50:18,951
what?

658
00:50:22,299 --> 00:50:24,503
you think that makes sense?

659
00:50:24,503 --> 00:50:28,539
you said you like me..

660
00:50:28,539 --> 00:50:32,267
can't you do that for me?

661
00:50:35,500 --> 00:50:38,942
I feel like..
I could just die..without Hye-ryun..

662
00:50:38,942 --> 00:50:41,722
I'm sorry, Jung-eun...

663
00:50:42,877 --> 00:50:43,926
die! you die!

664
00:50:43,926 --> 00:50:45,280
you're so bad, you die!

665
00:50:45,280 --> 00:50:47,008
die! you die!

666
00:50:47,008 --> 00:50:48,850
you better die!

667
00:50:48,850 --> 00:50:50,102
you're so bad!

668
00:50:50,102 --> 00:50:51,391
you die..

669
00:51:02,311 --> 00:51:05,812
( when you're holding me tight.. )

670
00:51:05,812 --> 00:51:09,613
( I can hear.. )

671
00:51:09,613 --> 00:51:16,476
( I can hear you breathing.. )

672
00:51:16,476 --> 00:51:19,985
( it feels so good.. )

673
00:51:19,985 --> 00:51:30,528
( I could almost cry.. )

674
00:51:35,107 --> 00:51:37,101
( a memorandum )

675
00:51:37,101 --> 00:51:39,704
( I, Kyung-min Lee, )

676
00:51:39,704 --> 00:51:42,681
( will marry Jung-eun Nam )

677
00:51:42,681 --> 00:51:46,144
( after I passed the bar exam. )

678
00:51:51,817 --> 00:51:58,820
( you're the biggest gift.. )

679
00:51:58,820 --> 00:52:06,126
( from the sky to me.. )

680
00:52:25,959 --> 00:52:27,940
Jung-eun,
give me some water..

681
00:52:28,526 --> 00:52:30,158
Jung-eun!

682
00:52:35,457 --> 00:52:36,778
Jung-eun..

683
00:52:39,967 --> 00:52:41,265
where is she?

684
00:52:59,189 --> 00:53:01,905
where has she gone to?

685
00:53:18,808 --> 00:53:20,673
why did you call me up?

686
00:53:20,673 --> 00:53:22,902
you know why, don't you?

687
00:53:22,902 --> 00:53:24,534
I know why?
I don't think so.

688
00:53:24,534 --> 00:53:26,894
I have no idea.

689
00:53:30,532 --> 00:53:35,094
I'll tell you what you wanna hear from me.

690
00:53:35,094 --> 00:53:37,843
Kyung-min & me are just friends.

691
00:53:37,843 --> 00:53:40,703
and he likes..

692
00:53:40,703 --> 00:53:44,167
nobody but you.

693
00:53:44,167 --> 00:53:46,421
nobody can replace you.

694
00:53:46,421 --> 00:53:48,411
nobody compares to you..

695
00:53:49,437 --> 00:53:51,191
are you satisfied now?

696
00:53:51,191 --> 00:53:52,682
by the way,

697
00:53:52,682 --> 00:53:56,439
why are you keeping him at your place?

698
00:53:57,248 --> 00:54:00,341
that's..

699
00:54:00,341 --> 00:54:03,954
that's because I borrowed some money from him.

700
00:54:03,954 --> 00:54:07,364
so he's staying at my place
until I pay the money back to him.

701
00:54:07,364 --> 00:54:09,950
that's all.

702
00:54:09,950 --> 00:54:11,725
is that all?

703
00:54:11,725 --> 00:54:12,735
yeah, that's all.

704
00:54:14,172 --> 00:54:16,064
you..

705
00:54:16,064 --> 00:54:19,207
you slept with him, right?

706
00:54:19,207 --> 00:54:21,460
say what?

707
00:54:21,460 --> 00:54:24,191
you really did?

708
00:54:25,166 --> 00:54:27,053
no, I didn't.

709
00:54:27,053 --> 00:54:29,643
you didn't?

710
00:54:29,643 --> 00:54:32,149
no.

711
00:54:33,478 --> 00:54:35,999
getting a guy
by sleeping with him..

712
00:54:35,999 --> 00:54:39,204
that's the worst thing a girl can do.

713
00:54:39,204 --> 00:54:41,132
it's very sad
there's still a girl like you.

714
00:54:41,132 --> 00:54:42,710
ya!

715
00:54:42,710 --> 00:54:43,790
what?

716
00:54:43,790 --> 00:54:46,042
you wanna hit me on my face again?

717
00:54:46,042 --> 00:54:49,419
you already forgot why you came here?

718
00:54:51,560 --> 00:54:55,676
I will forgive Kyung-min this time.

719
00:54:56,449 --> 00:54:59,020
what a sad story you're making..

720
00:54:59,020 --> 00:55:01,884
I didn't know that
you like Kyung-min this much.

721
00:55:02,906 --> 00:55:04,509
no. not any more.

722
00:55:04,509 --> 00:55:07,032
I gave him up.
he's so hopeless.

723
00:55:07,032 --> 00:55:08,577
you & Kyung-min..

724
00:55:08,577 --> 00:55:11,736
both are hopeless jerks like garbage.

725
00:55:12,941 --> 00:55:14,263
I gotta go.

726
00:55:14,263 --> 00:55:15,909
I'm busy.

727
00:55:15,909 --> 00:55:18,002
bye.

728
00:55:39,810 --> 00:55:41,414
Kyung-min!

729
00:55:41,414 --> 00:55:43,159
Hye-ryun!

730
00:55:43,159 --> 00:55:44,934
Hye-ryun..

731
00:55:44,934 --> 00:55:46,476
sorry for yesterday's thing..

732
00:55:46,476 --> 00:55:48,014
I'm sorry. I apologize.

733
00:55:48,014 --> 00:55:51,422
I didn't have chance
to say goodbye to Jung-eun, so..

734
00:55:51,422 --> 00:55:53,456
I came to her place
to say goodbye and..

735
00:55:53,456 --> 00:55:54,868
she made dinner for me..

736
00:55:54,868 --> 00:55:58,552
it's alright.
I met Jung-eun and she cleared my misunderstanding.

737
00:55:58,552 --> 00:56:01,552
Jung-eun..
she came here?

738
00:56:01,552 --> 00:56:04,184
she explained the situation to me.

739
00:56:04,184 --> 00:56:06,864
I think I misunderstood something.

740
00:56:08,216 --> 00:56:10,897
she seems to like you so much.

741
00:56:10,897 --> 00:56:14,043
you asked her to see me, right?
oh, she just did what you want her to do.

742
00:56:14,969 --> 00:56:17,599
I felt sorry for her..

743
00:56:17,599 --> 00:56:21,037
I think she'd better find another guy
who fits her status.

744
00:56:21,037 --> 00:56:23,964
now she learned that you don't like her.
that's actually good for her.

745
00:56:23,964 --> 00:56:25,194
she can find another guy now.

746
00:56:25,194 --> 00:56:27,484
oh, she's just a stupid idiot!

747
00:56:28,997 --> 00:56:32,751
( I'm sorry.. )

748
00:56:32,751 --> 00:56:36,514
( don't cry.. )

749
00:56:36,514 --> 00:56:44,320
( now I'm back here for you.. )

750
00:56:44,320 --> 00:56:47,970
( now I know that.. )

751
00:56:47,970 --> 00:56:51,811
( I can't be happy.. )

752
00:56:51,811 --> 00:56:59,418
( without you.. )

753
00:56:59,418 --> 00:57:03,157
( when you're holding me tight.. )

754
00:57:03,157 --> 00:57:06,992
( I can hear.. )

755
00:57:06,992 --> 00:57:14,710
( I can hear you breathing.. )

756
00:57:14,710 --> 00:57:18,511
( it feels so good.. )

757
00:57:18,511 --> 00:57:29,949
( I could almost cry.. )

758
00:57:29,949 --> 00:57:33,736
( now I'm back here for you.. )

759
00:57:33,736 --> 00:57:37,515
( I can see your tears here.. )

760
00:57:37,515 --> 00:57:39,996
( it's breaking my heart.. )

761
00:57:40,150 --> 00:57:41,862
hi,

762
00:57:45,173 --> 00:57:48,994
( it's breaking my heart.. )

763
00:57:48,994 --> 00:57:52,799
( but now it's okay.. )

764
00:57:52,799 --> 00:58:00,391
( you're the biggest gift.. )

765
00:58:00,391 --> 00:58:03,646
( from the sky to me.. )

766
00:58:04,722 --> 00:58:07,757
I like you..

767
00:58:08,003 --> 00:58:15,609
( now I'm back here for you.. )

768
00:58:15,609 --> 00:58:23,236
( I can see your tears here.. )

769
00:58:23,236 --> 00:58:27,043
( it's breaking my heart.. )

770
00:58:27,043 --> 00:58:30,892
( but now it's okay.. )

771
00:58:30,892 --> 00:58:38,527
( you're the biggest gift.. )

772
00:58:38,527 --> 00:58:54,414
( from  the sky to me.. )

773
00:59:00,654 --> 00:59:03,367
Jung-eun..

774
00:59:27,933 --> 00:59:30,115
you idiot..

775
00:59:33,391 --> 00:59:35,099
how could..

776
00:59:35,099 --> 00:59:38,161
how could you really do that?

777
00:59:55,761 --> 00:59:57,929
Jung-eun..

778
00:59:57,929 --> 01:00:00,955
I like you..

779
01:00:05,672 --> 01:00:07,657
I think it's very hard..

780
01:00:07,657 --> 01:00:11,486
to like somebody.

781
01:00:11,486 --> 01:00:15,334
it's very difficult for me..

782
01:00:15,334 --> 01:00:19,426
nobody taught me
what is love & what it's like to like someone..

783
01:00:19,426 --> 01:00:21,822
same for you, right?

784
01:00:21,822 --> 01:00:25,053
it's the fault of the education system!

785
01:00:25,053 --> 01:00:27,949
what is calculus,
what is 'hello' & 'hi'..

786
01:00:27,949 --> 01:00:30,508
those are not very important, you know.

787
01:00:30,508 --> 01:00:31,825
what's important is..

788
01:00:31,825 --> 01:00:33,034
'what is love?'

789
01:00:33,034 --> 01:00:35,247
and 'what's the difference between love & like'.

790
01:00:35,247 --> 01:00:38,190
they should teach it,
don't you think so?

791
01:00:46,283 --> 01:00:48,377
Jung-eun..

792
01:00:51,740 --> 01:00:55,636
I'm..

793
01:00:55,636 --> 01:00:57,618
Kyung-min,

794
01:00:57,618 --> 01:01:01,216
let's put an end to it.

795
01:01:05,867 --> 01:01:08,657
let's get apart.

796
01:01:22,203 --> 01:01:23,394
Jung-eun,

797
01:01:23,394 --> 01:01:25,831
yesterday's thing was..

798
01:01:25,831 --> 01:01:30,675
Kyung-min,

799
01:01:30,675 --> 01:01:34,956
it's not because I got mad at you..

800
01:01:34,956 --> 01:01:39,769
and I'm not saying this to threaten you..

801
01:01:39,769 --> 01:01:44,096
I'm serious now..

802
01:01:44,096 --> 01:01:47,465
please get out of my place..

803
01:01:47,819 --> 01:01:50,417
Jung-eun..

804
01:01:50,962 --> 01:01:52,771
can you imagine..

805
01:01:52,771 --> 01:01:56,556
how I felt when I saw Hye-ryun?

806
01:02:01,214 --> 01:02:06,229
I did the last thing I can do.

807
01:02:06,229 --> 01:02:12,345
so..

808
01:02:12,345 --> 01:02:14,732
you think about it, and..

809
01:02:14,732 --> 01:02:18,584
tell me when you're gonna get out of my place..

810
01:02:57,318 --> 01:03:00,700
Jung-eun : Da-bin Jung
Kyung-min : Rae-won Kim

811
01:03:00,700 --> 01:03:03,991
Hye-ryun : Jung-yoon Choi
Dong-june : Hyun-woo Lee

